{"id":220297,"date":[{"year":1951,"month":3,"day":28}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"长街短巷","genre":"","count":"290","ytitle":"","mtitle":"爱国摊贩·爱国公约","ftitle":"","authors":["沈翼燕"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"随着全上海人民一道，在各单位爱国公约纷纷签订的同时，邑庙区的摊贩们也组织了起来，他们动员了全部爱国不落人后的摊贩同志们，订出切合实际的爱国公约；为了坚决执行起见，特把这行动纲领漆在复兴东路翁家衖菜场旁边的墙上。公约极通俗，如下:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摆摊要领照"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"木棚要拆掉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"货物摆整齐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随时要打扫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三天不出摊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"执照要报销"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"违反本公约"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无照要报告"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"执照随身带"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"物价照公议"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不卖烂东西"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要向组长报"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纠察来纠正"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开会来检讨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摊位照编号"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或用镜架吊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"交易不欺骗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"食物要加罩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十天不出摊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"应该听劝导"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能随便调"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秩序要遵守"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对客要礼貌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不开收音机"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要向政府报"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公约要遵守"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摊基照规定"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"交通要顾到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清洁要保持"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不敲不高叫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摊子如不摆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"法令更重要"}]}